snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to share what johnny depp fans are demanding which is why amber in danger.

Johnny Depp was set to return as Gellert Grindelwald in Fantastic Beasts 3, but recently came under intense scrutiny during his highly publicized divorce from Amber Heard. Depp has been charged with domestic violence. He denied the allegations, but lost a high-profile defamation case against a newspaper that branded him a "woman hitter." franchise. Depp also lost his other role better known as Captain Jack Sparrow in Disney's Pirates of the Caribbean franchise. On the other hand, Amber Heard has started filming for Aquaman 2.
